<h2 id="name">Name</h2>
<p>The <code>BlogPost</code> component renders a blog post layout with chapters and a summary view option. It can display detailed content with Markdown formatting using the <code>MarkdownTextField</code> component.</p>

<hr />

<h2 id="properties">Properties</h2>
<p>The <code>BlogPost</code> component has the following properties:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Title</strong> (string, required): The title of the blog post.</li>
    <li><strong>Subtitle</strong> (string): An optional subtitle for the blog post.</li>
    <li><strong>DateOfPublish</strong> (string, required): The publication date of the blog post.</li>
    <li><strong>Author</strong> (string, required): The author of the blog post.</li>
    <li><strong>Content</strong> (List&lt;BlogPostContent&gt;, required): A list of chapters where each item contains the chapter title and Markdown content.</li>
    <li><strong>JustSummary</strong> (bool): Displays only the chapter titles in a summary mode.</li>
    <li><strong>MaxWidth</strong> (string): Sets the maximum width of the component. Defaults to "100%".</li>
</ul>

